  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Le Miramonti is a traditional, Alpine hotel situated on the riverside in the centre of La Thuile. Modern, high quality facilities now blend with a cosy mountain atmosphere and the use of traditional wood and stone create a luxurious mountain chalet feel. Facilities include spacious bar and lounge area, reading room and attractive restaurant. The wellness centre with sauna, small indoor pool/whirlpool, steam room and experience showers (pay locally) is the perfect place to relax after a long day skiing.</p>]]></description>
